          "interaction": {
            "id": "north-sidewalk-kid-talk",
            "speaker": "Sidewalk Kid",
            "duration_seconds": 2.8,
            "complete_objective": "collect_first_witness",
            "lines": [
              "The Sidewalk Kid points at Bosch, then at the curb where the other Bosch apparently stood.",
              "\"He had your face and a cleaner story. Said 'Swag is eternal' like a slogan he found in somebody else's pocket.\"",
              "Everybody repeated it before anyone asked if you were here.",
              "Sal's kiosk can make proof before gossip grows paperwork."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "north-neighbor-home",
          "definition": "neighbor-wander",
          "source_id": "north-neighbor-home",
          "wander_box_tiles": [
            29,
            11,
            30,
            12
          ],
          "interaction": {
            "id": "north-neighbor-home-talk",
            "speaker": "North Neighbor",
            "duration_seconds": 1.9,
            "lines": [
              "Your terminal phrase got here before you did.",
              "The other Bosch walked like he was following arrows only he could see."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "north-office-kid",
          "definition": "kid-idle-south",
          "source_id": "north-office-kid",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "north-office-kid-talk",
            "speaker": "Compliance Kid",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "The public Bosch is easier to process because he never interrupts the form.",
              "The Public Version Clique says that is basically citizenship."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "north-shop-neighbor",
          "definition": "neighbor-idle-south",
          "source_id": "north-shop-neighbor",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "north-shop-neighbor-talk",
            "speaker": "Route Clerk",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "complete_objective": "collect_first_witness",
            "lines": [
              "Gate brief: proof first, witness second, park rumors last.",
              "Refuse the clique before the classifier reads the easy Bosch."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "shop-front-neighbor",
          "definition": "neighbor-idle-south",
          "source_id": "shop-front-neighbor",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "shop-front-neighbor-talk",
            "speaker": "Shop Front Neighbor",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "Two flashes hit Signal Park.",
              "North spread the rumor; south made people act like it was already settled."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "burger-line-kid",
          "definition": "kid-route",
          "source_id": "burger-line-kid",
          "route_tiles": [
            [
              21,
              25
            ],
            [
              22,
              25
            ],
            [
              21,
              25
            ],
            [
              20,
              25
            ]
          ],
          "interaction": {
            "id": "burger-line-kid-talk",
            "speaker": "Burger Line Kid",
            "duration_seconds": 1.9,
            "lines": [
              "The line only moves when everybody faces the counter.",
              "The other Bosch knew where to stand."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "townhall-neighbor",
          "definition": "neighbor-idle-south",
          "source_id": "townhall-neighbor",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "townhall-neighbor-talk",
            "speaker": "Town Hall Neighbor",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "Witness, proof, public refusal, parks, classifier.",
              "Keep the messy order where the gate can read it."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "east-shop-kid",
          "definition": "kid-idle-south",
          "source_id": "east-shop-kid",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "east-shop-kid-talk",
            "speaker": "East Shop Kid",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "The sign by town hall changed overnight.",
              "It points at the station like your name is already on the schedule."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "southwest-kid",
          "definition": "kid-idle-south",
          "source_id": "southwest-kid",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "southwest-kid-talk",
            "speaker": "Southwest Kid",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "South park is shorter and meaner.",
              "It asks you to react before you can think, then calls that consent."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "south-home-neighbor",
          "definition": "neighbor-idle-south",
          "source_id": "south-home-neighbor",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "south-home-neighbor-talk",
            "speaker": "South Home Neighbor",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "Everyone is pretending the public Bosch is just a joke.",
              "It stopped being funny when the flyers knew your room."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "south-office-kid",
          "definition": "kid-idle-south",
          "source_id": "south-office-kid",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "south-office-kid-talk",
            "speaker": "South Office Kid",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "If your HP dips, regroup before the next fight.",
              "The route records courage and panic the same way, but your body knows the difference."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "southeast-neighbor",
          "definition": "neighbor-idle-south",
          "source_id": "southeast-neighbor",
          "interaction": {
            "id": "southeast-neighbor-talk",
            "speaker": "Neighbor",
            "duration_seconds": 1.8,
            "lines": [
              "Oh, hey. Do you ever think about doors?",
              "Anyway, I am late for the post office."
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "woods-neighbor",
          "definition": "neighbor-wander",
          "source_id": "woods-neighbor",
          "wander_box_tiles": [
            33,
            45,
            35,
            46
